Package agents

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Car
    Agent that represents a car.
    CarMonitored
    The car that is supervised.
    CarNoneLearning
    It's an extended class of car just with the purpose of handling the debug messages in a different way and to enable the choice of a different icon in the repast display, such that it can be easily distinguished in the space from the other cars.
    CarSerializable
    Serializable class to save the car information so that in a next time the car has some knowledge about the world.
    CarShortLearning
    It's an extended class of car just with the purpose of handling the debug messages in a different way and to enable the choice of a different icon in the repast display, such that it can be easily distinguished in the space from the other cars.
    City
    Agent that represents the city structure and displays in the space the image correspondent to the map.
    Radio
    Agent that is responsible to communicate the transit flow to the cars in the same container.
    RoadMonitor
    Agent that is responsible to track the transit in the road that it's associated with and communicate any change in the transit flow to the radio.
    Semaphore
    Agent that represents a semaphore.
    SemaphoreGreen
    Extended class of the semaphore just with the purpose of representing the different possible semaphore lights in the space.
    SemaphoreManager
    Agent that it's responsible to manage the semaphores in an intersection and switch the lights after a certain time.
    SemaphoreRed
    Extended class of the semaphore just with the purpose of representing the different possible semaphore lights in the space.
    SemaphoreYellow
    Extended class of the semaphore just with the purpose of representing the different possible semaphore lights in the space.
